84AC28609EDE40BD98673454BD5B39D6.description:
I can invite community members to participate in ASL or Deaf related school
events. Examples: A Deaf guest speaker addressing career options; providing ASL tutoring;
giving a demonstration of an ASL story.

4FB6FC4735FA47109A6DC67D1788E9F3.description:
I can use ASL to plan activities that benefit the school or community. Examples:
Organizing a school fundraising event with an ASL theme; hosting a Deaf art show;
performing ASL poetry at school talent nights.

144401BA094446B096ED0BC338FF399B.description:
I can expand their knowledge in other subject areas on topics of personal
interests. Examples: Identifying the parts of a vehicle; learning about personal hygiene;
discussing technology and technical equipment.

81E4C761D3F444EF88A7B85175E571C0.description:
I can demonstrate an understanding of various communication strategies used by
Deaf individuals in their daily lives. Examples: Using a videophone; placing a video relay call;
texting and / or using ASL to communicate on a mobile phone.
